_sText:
fy_pool_day is a port of the fy_pool_day from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

Remake of the famous "fy pool day" map from Counter-Strike 1.6.

Fight Yard objective (fy_) :

Grab a weapon on the floor and fight !

Impossible mission : plant the bomb.

A Switchable version has been published here :

http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=832043432

In this version, you can switch in real-time between the CS 1.6 and CSGO version of the map.

Credits:

CS:GO remake by leplubodeslapin

Additional content by Bendix8 and Nicoreda

Original map created by Squall
